ugins/\">Achieving WPML compatibility for your themes and plugins</a>. It easily tests compatibility with WPML and helps you quickly make your theme or plugin <strong>Multilingual Ready</strong>.</p>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center\">Storefront theme</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"http://www.woothemes.com/storefront/\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-340493\" src=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/storefront.png\" alt=\"ekho\" width=\"590\" height=\"300\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>A free WordPress theme offering deep integration with WooCommerce.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"http://www.woothemes.com/storefront/\" target=\"_blank\">Download Storefront theme</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center\">T-ONE theme</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"http://themeforest.net/item/tone-clean-minimal-wordpress-theme/7602385\"><img src=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/tone.png\" alt=\"ekho\" width=\"590\" height=\"300\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>Creative &#038; responsive WordPress Theme featuring clean and minimal design suitable for any studio, agencies, portfolio, graphic designers, etc.. Powered with Twitter Bootstrap &#038; Redux Framework. It can be customized easily to suit your wishes.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"http://themeforest.net/item/tone-clean-minimal-wordpress-theme/7602385\">Purchase T-ONE theme</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center\">Cardinal Theme</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"http://themeforest.net/item/cardinal-wordpress-theme/8070889\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-340493\" src=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/cardinal.png\" alt=\"ekho\" width=\"590\" height=\"300\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>Cardinal is mobile ready, c