(28,	1,	'2014-11-03 05:03:03',	'2014-11-03 05:03:03',	'Mr. Hong Tran has nearly 17 years of experiences in international software business. With technology and management background, Hong has involved in many different roles and functions: software programmer, technical architect, solution consultant, project manager, Business Development, Marketing, R&amp;D, Human Resources, Training, Quality Management, General Management. With a wide range of experience in software, Hong has supported clients from many countries on IT strategy and solutions. Hong is currently the vice president of TMA Solutions.',	'Hong Tran-Phuc',	'',	'publish',	'open',	'open',	'',	'hong-tran-phuc',	'',	'',	'2015-01-21 17:10:51',	'2015-01-21 17:10:51',	'',	0,	'https://nhunguyen-nhunguyen1980.c9.io/Vnito/?post_type=speaker&#038;p=28',	8,	'speaker',	'',	0),
