(30,	1,	'2014-11-03 05:03:37',	'2014-11-03 05:03:37',	'Mr Toan has more than 18 years experience in software &amp; IT industry, particularly on those systems related to telecommunication, paging, customer management, billing, HR &amp; training development, quality &amp; process management, and public relations. Toan\'s specific areas of expertise include implementation and management of corporate systems based on the international standards ISO-9001/ISO27001/CMMI/RUP.\r\n\r\nToan currently is Vice President of Global CyberSoft Vietnam - one of the largest US-based software companies in Vietnam with over 850 software engineers to provide software development outsourcing and consulting services to companies worldwide.',	'Toan Ngo-Van',	'',	'publish',	'open',	'open',	'',	'toan-ngo-van',	'',	'',	'2015-01-26 12:08:56',	'2015-01-26 12:08:56',	'',	0,	'https://nhunguyen-nhunguyen1980.c9.io/Vnito/?post_type=speaker&#038;p=30',	20,	'speaker',	'',	0),
