(34,	1,	'2014-11-03 05:04:55',	'2014-11-03 05:04:55',	'Cuong La-Manh is the Managing Director of Luxoft Vietnam Company, a subsidiary of the global leading IT Solution &amp; Service Provider Luxoft (NYSE:LXFT US). Cuong is responsible for overall operations and growth of Luxoft global Delivery Center, relationships with key customers and strategic partnerships within Vietnam country.\r\n\r\nCuong has more than 20 years of experience working in the IT and software industry at major Vietnamese and International companies. His deep knowledge of domestic as well as international markets supported by strong hands-on managerial experience greatly contributed to the successful startup and growth of Luxoft in the region.\r\n\r\nCuong holds an Engineer Degree from HCMC University of Agriculture and Forestry, an MBA Degree from Open University Malaysia and has accomplished a number of various international business courses in Software Engineering and Management',	'Cuong La-Manh',	'',	'publish',	'open',	'open',	'',	'cuong-la-manh',	'',	'',	'2015-01-21 17:10:27',	'2015-01-21 17:10:27',	'',	0,	'https://nhunguyen-nhunguyen1980.c9.io/Vnito/?post_type=speaker&#038;p=34',	3,	'speaker',	'',	0),
