(59,	1,	'2014-11-15 10:10:41',	'2014-11-15 10:10:41',	'<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\">Why should you consider sponsorship?</h1>\r\n<div class=\"csRow\">\r\n<div class=\"csColumnGap\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; float: left; width: 1.56%;\"><img src=\"https://nhunguyen-nhunguyen1980.c9.io/Vnito/wp-content/plugins/advanced-wp-columns/assets/js/plugins/views/img/1x1-pixel.png\" alt=\"\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"csColumn\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; float: left; width: 45.2%;\" data-csid=\"76d4df6a-3fb4-b95f-aa4a-d4f599b5e2ab\" data-cswidth=\"45.2%\" data-csendpoint=\"448.5\" data-csstartpoint=\"15\">\r\n<h2>Access to global market</h2>\r\nVNITO  is an effective business matching platform for Vietnamese IT Outsourcing vendors and buyers. As a sponsor, you will gain access to a highly targeted buyers including companies, government representatives and software product companies from 15-20 countries such as the US, UK, Japan... Additionally, this is a chance for you to engage in-person with a large numbers of local industry leaders.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"csColumnGap\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; float: left; width: 6.56%;\"><img src=\"https://nhunguyen-nhunguyen1980.c9.io/Vnito/wp-content/plugins/advanced-wp-columns/assets/js/plugins/views/img/1x1-pixel.png\" alt=\"\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"csColumn\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; float: left; width: 45.2%;\" data-csid=\"d1dc1cae-daa7-6645-9ee0-1b7b6e4e82d6\" data-cswidth=\"45.2%\" data-csendpoint=\"945\" data-csstartpoint=\"511.5\">\r\n<h2>Global brand visibility</h2>\r\nAs part of the sponsorship package, you will have multiple opportunities to promote your brand through the VNITO website, emails, and social media. At the conference, sponsors receive special brand promotion through conference document, media, ... You can reserve an exhibition booth to showcase your products and services.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"csColumnGap\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; float: left; width: 1.56%;\"><img src=\"https://nhunguyen-nhunguyen1980.c9.io/Vnito/wp-content/plugins/advanced-wp-columns/assets/js/plugins/views/img/1x1-pixel.png\" alt=\"\" /></div>\r\n<div style=\"clear: both; float: none; display: block; visibility: hidden; width: 0px; font-size: 0px; line-height: 0;\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>Diamond Sponsorship</strong></span></td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>300,000,000 VND</strong></span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>Platinum Sponsorship</strong></span></td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>100,000,000 VND</strong></span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>Gold Sponsorship</strong></span></td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>60,000,000 VND</strong></span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Silver Sponsorship</span></td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">40,000,000 VND</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Bronze Sponsorship</span></td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">20,000,000 VND</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Meal, Item, Gift and Event Sponsorship</span></td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">10,000,000 VND</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Awards Ceremony and Gala Dinner Sponsorship</span></td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">30,000,000 VND</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p style=\"width: 620px; margin: 0px auto; text-align: left;\">Contact us directly at (+84) 937 888 293 or <a href=\"mailto:contact@vnito.org\" target=\"_blank\">co