(343,	1,	'2015-01-06 11:55:04',	'2015-01-06 11:55:04',	'Please put the initial info below as the different sponsoring packages we offer at the moment. More details will come later. Currency unit is in VND. We target mostly to outsourcing vendors in Vietnam as sponsors.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Diamond Sponsorship</td>\r\n<td>300,000,000 VND</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Platinum Sponsorship</td>\r\n<td>100,000,000 VND</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Gold Sponsorship</td>\r\n<td>60,000,000 VND</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Silver Sponsorship</td>\r\n<td>40,000,000 VND</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Bronze Sponsorship</td>\r\n<td>20,000,000 VND</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Meal, Item, Gift and Event Sponsorship</td>\r\n<td>10,000,000 VND</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Awards Ceremony and Gala Dinner Sponsorship</td>\r\n<td>30,000,000 VND</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<h3>Why you should consider sponsorship?</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Access to global market.</strong> VNITO is an effective business matching platform for Vietnamese IT Outsourcing vendors and buyers. As a sponsor, you will gain access to a highly targeted buyers including companies, government representatives and software product companies from 15-20 countries such as the US, UK, Japan... Additionally, this is a chance for you to engage in-person with a large numbers of local industry leaders.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Global brand visibility.</strong> As part of the sponsorship package, you will have multiple opportunities to promote your brand through the VNITO website, emails, and social media. At the conference, sponsors receive special brand promotion through conference document, media, ... You can reserve an exhibition booth to showcase your products and services.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nContact us directly at or to discuss the full complement of sponsor benefits or fill in the form below. You will be in touch shortly.\r\n<h3>Register your attendance form</h3>\r\n[contact-form-7 i