(368,	1,	'2015-01-07 08:28:12',	'2015-01-07 08:28:12',	'Vu Lam is the CEO and Founder of KMS. He owns the vision and global delivery operations for KMS. He was one of the co-founders of KMS with the belief that there should be a better way to provide software outsourcing, for his clients as well as for the engineers. He was confident that he knew the way, so he started the journey of KMS with his partners to prove it. To be successful, Vu knows that he needs to recognize the talent and strengths of the team, and allow them to utilize it to achieve success for themselves and for KMS clients.\r\n\r\nVu co-founded Paragon Solutions, Inc., a US-based technology consulting company with international development centers in Bangalore, India and Ho Chi Minh City, Vietnam. His establishment and guidance of Paragon Solutions Vietnam (PSV) led to his recognition as a pioneer of the Vietnam IT industry. Following the acquisition of Paragon by First Consulting Group (FCG), a NASDAQ traded company, Vu led FCG\'s Global Shared-Services group and led the growth of the organization from 400 to 1,300+ resources. Vu is also currently a Board member of several IT startup companies.',	'Vu Lam',	'',	'publish',	'open',	'open',	'',	'vu-lam',	'',	'',	'2015-01-21 17:04:35',	'2015-01-21 17:04:35',	'',	0,	'https://nhunguyen-nhunguyen1980.c9.io/Vnito/?post_type=speaker&#038;p=368',	28,	'speaker',	'',	0),
