(383,	1,	'2015-01-07 08:36:49',	'2015-01-07 08:36:49',	'Mr. Jens Jonasson has been within the IT-industry for more than 25 years. He has gained a wide range of experience within software development and testing, project-management as well as C-level position as CTO and CIO both on public and private enterprises. Jens field of experience spans through logistics, telecom, hotels/travel and Internet-startups to mention some. For the last ten years Jens has been working with offshore outsourcing, ITO, and has a wide range of experience from different outsourcing-locations. Jens has also international experience from working closely with USA, UK, South East Asia and northern european countries.\r\n\r\nJens primary target today is boosting clients with energy helping them setup effective corporate-processes aligned with outsourcing of technology services offshore.',	'Jens Jonasson',	'',	'publish',	'open',	'open',	'',	'jens-jonasson',	'',	'',	'2015-01-21 17:06:45',	'2015-01-21 17:06:45',	'',	0,	'https://nhunguyen-nhunguyen1980.c9.io/Vnito/?post_type=speaker&#038;p=383',	8,	'speaker',	'',	0),
