(385,	1,	'2015-01-07 08:39:46',	'2015-01-07 08:39:46',	'Steve Roatch is the founder and CEO of Twentyseven Global, a software engineering company with offices in Kansas City and Denver.  Steve, a twenty-five year software industry veteran, started this business with the vision of creating a game-changing suite of services for software companies and information technology-intensive businesses.  Prior to forming Twentyseven Global, Steve held positions as the Chief Operating Officer of IntraISP Software Solutions, a telecom billing and customer relationship management software provider and Managing Partner at the global consulting firm Accenture.\r\n\r\nSteve has done business globally, with clients in Europe, Asia, Australia, North and South America.  Steve is an active angel investor, mentoring and investing through several local accelerators, angel networks, and VC funds. He enjoys travel and experiencing the rich cultural diversity the world has to offer.  Steve has a BS in Electrical Engineering and a BA in Economics, both from Northwestern University',	'Steve Roatch',	'',	'publish',	'open',	'open',	'',	'steve-roatch',	'',	'',	'2015-01-26 12:10:38',	'2015-01-26 12:10:38',	'',	0,	'https://nhunguyen-nhunguyen1980.c9.io/Vnito/?post_type=speaker&#038;p=385',	19,	'speaker',	'',	0),
