(390,	1,	'2015-01-07 08:41:29',	'2015-01-07 08:41:29',	'Mr. James Galvin is a tech CEO with 15 years experience in the industry, spanning a number of disciplines including Software Development, Security, IT Infrastructure, and Big Data / Analytics.  He is involved in several tech startups in Ireland, USA, UK, and Singapore, both as a co-founder and as a mentor.  In 2007, James founded Glandore Systems, a provider of HR Technology solutions that is now the largest Irish company in Vietnam.  Glandore\'s flagship offering, vsource.io, allows companies to increase throughput in their recruitment process by accessing smart technology powered by offshore human resources in Ho Chi Minh City.  James is currently the Chairman of the Irish Business Association of Vietnam.',	'James Galvin',	'',	'publish',	'open',	'open',	'',	'james-galvin',	'',	'',	'2015-01-21 17:06:35',	'2015-01-21 17:06:35',	'',	0,	'https://nhunguyen-nhunguyen1980.c9.io/Vnito/?post_type=speaker&#038;p=390',	8,	'speaker',	'',	0),
