(457,	1,	'2015-01-09 04:28:47',	'2015-01-09 04:28:47',	'Bob Jackson has been involved in various areas of technology for over 30 years. he was fortunate to be at the forefront of changes from manual to automated systems, copper to optical transmission, modems to networks and the rise and rise of the internet.\r\n\r\nBob has a background in programming and has also worked in IT recruitment, Software and Hardware solution sales, with Telecommunications, ISP and Cable operators and at the forefront of LAN and WAN development.\r\n\r\nHe has assisted many organisations in their digital development, both in the Australia and New Zealand region and in the 16 other countries that he has been fortunate to have been deployed to.',	'Bob Jackson',	'',	'inherit',	'open',	'open',	'',	'400-revision-v1',	'',	'',	'2015-01-09 04:28:47',	'2015-01-09 04:28:47',	'',	400,	'https://nhunguyen-nhunguyen1980.c9.io/Vnito/2015/01/400-revision-v1/',	0,	'revision',	'',	0),
