(463,	1,	'2015-01-09 04:45:13',	'2015-01-09 04:45:13',	'<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"left-col\">Name</td>\r\n<td>Nguyen Cong Ai</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"left-col\">Position</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Partner – Ho Chi Minh Office, Tax &amp; Corporate Services</li>\r\n	<li>Head of Market Entry Group</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"left-col\">Qualifications</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>PhD in International Business, University of Economics, Bratislava, Slovak Republic</li>\r\n	<li>MA in International Economics</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"left-col\">Experiences</td>\r\n<td>PhD Nguyen Cong Ai has been working for KPMG since 1998, in Slovakia and Vietnam. He has been involved in providing Market Entry advisory services to many international companies entering Vietnam.. PhD Nguyen Cong Ai has extensive experience in conducting market entry studies, location analysis, commercial due diligence and assistance with Investment licensing and post-license compliance.Being in contact with Government Agencies and Business Communities throughout Vietnam for years, Ai has extensive business and government network.Dr Ai’s clients include many of leading companies in Vietnam and overseas: Petro Vietnam Fertilizer and Chemicals Company, Kookmin Bank, Lotte Mart, Masan Group Corporation, Vietnam Southern Food General Corporation, Mitsubishi Corporation, Deutsche Bank AG, Sharp Corporation.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>',	'Nguyen Cong Ai',	'',	'inherit',	'open',	'open',	'',	'415-revision-v1',	'',	'',	'2015-01-09 04:45:13',	'2015-01-09 04:45:13',	'',	415,	'https://nhunguyen-nhunguyen1980.c9.io/Vnito/2015/01/415-revision-v1/',	0,	'revision',	'',	0),
(464,	1,	'2015-01-09 04:47:52',	'2015-01-09 04:47:52',	'Mr. Jens Jonasson has been within the IT-industry for more than 25 years. He has gained a wide range of experience within software development and testing, project-management as well as C-level position as CTO and CIO both on public and private enterprises. Jens field of experience spans through logistics, telecom, hotels/travel and Internet-startups to mention some. For the last ten years Jens has been working with offshore outsourcing, ITO, and has a wide range of experience from different outsourcing-locations. Jens has also international experience from working closely with USA, UK, South East Asia and northern european countries.\r\n\r\nJens primary target today is boosting clients with energy helping them setup effective corporate-processes aligned with outsourcing of technology services offshore.',	'Jens Jonasson',	'',	'inherit',	'open',	'open',	'',	'383-revision-v1',	'',	'',	'2015-01-09 04:47:52',	'2015-01-09 04:47:52',	'',	383,	'https://nhunguyen-nhunguyen1980.c9.io/Vnito/2015/01/383-revision-v1/',	0,	'revision',	'',	0),
