(513,	1,	'2015-01-09 08:22:54',	'2015-01-09 08:22:54',	'Mr. An Mai has been working in ICT industry for more than 18 years. He has extensive experience in setting up and operating Offshore Development Centers for enterprises from early-stage to Fortune 500. An also has international working experience in USA, Canada and APAC countries. He is a serial entrepreneur and involved in several startups in mobile application and IT service fields. In 2008, An co-founded IMT Solutions, a technology service firm focusing on providing software offshore services for Independent Software Vendors (ISV) and small and medium enterprises globally. An obtained his master degrees in both engineering and business administration. An is one of the early adopters of Agile Scrum in Vietnam.',	'An Mai-Hoai',	'',	'publish',	'open',	'open',	'',	'mai-hoai',	'',	'',	'2015-01-21 17:10:21',	'2015-01-21 17:10:21',	'',	0,	'https://nhunguyen-nhunguyen1980.c9.io/Vnito/?post_type=speaker&#038;p=513',	1,	'speaker',	'',	0),
