(519,	1,	'2015-01-09 08:23:37',	'2015-01-09 08:23:37',	'Hai has graduated from University of Economics in HCM (UEH) city in 1985 and worked as an economic expert in export-import area at a SOE in HCM city. Six years later, moved to the Saigon Jewelry Company (SJC) and appointed to be the Business Manager and Representative of SJC in a Joint Venture entity with Hong Kong. Hai took the Master of Development Economics under Vietnam-the Netherlands program offered at UEH from 1995-1998.\r\n\r\nAfter six years working at SJC, Hai moved to Hochiminh Export Processing Zone Authority (HEPZA) and appointed to be a Vice Rector of the College belonged to HEPZA since 1999. Receiving Vietnamese Government Scholarship, Hai went to University of Illinois at Chicago (UIC), USA for Ph.D. study since 2004. Returning home in early 2008 and starting – up the Gold Exchange named VGB, Hai made VGB good value during 2008-2010. In Oct. 2010, Hai took and invested in Viendong College and has built the long-term reputation for Viendong College. Besides teaching at Viendong College, Hai is also a financial expert and regularly appears on such outstanding newspapers as Tuoitre, Thanhnien, HTV, VTV.',	'Hai Tran-Thanh',	'',	'publish',	'open',	'open',	'',	'hai-tran-thanh',	'',	'',	'2015-01-27 17:23:29',	'2015-01-27 17:23:29',	'',	0,	'https://nhunguyen-nhunguyen1980.c9.io/Vnito/?post_type=speaker&#038;p=519',	7,	'speaker',	'',	0),
