(533,	1,	'2015-01-09 08:27:23',	'2015-01-09 08:27:23',	'Viet Hung is the Managing Director of KMS Technology Vietnam where he is responsible for the overall operations and growth of the organization. He was one of the co-founders of KMS Technology with the urge to build a workplace where people can grow and become successful. During his journey with KMS, Hung finds that his work is much easier due to the fact that his partners and co-workers at KMS are highly talented individuals, who share with him many values and most importantly the dream to build a great company.\r\n\r\nViet Hung began his career as a software developer. Then, grew through variety of positions including business analyst, project manager, and engineering manager in the top outsourcing firms in HCMC, Vietnam.\r\n\r\nViet Hung received a BS degree from Ho Chi Minh University of Technology, majored in Information Technology. He completed his Executive MBA Program at Shidler School of Business (University of Hawaii at Manoa) in 2009.',	'Hung Nguyen-Viet',	'',	'publish',	'open',	'open',	'',	'hung-nguyen-viet',	'',	'',	'2015-01-21 17:09:46',	'2015-01-21 17:09:46',	'',	0,	'https://nhunguyen-nhunguyen1980.c9.io/Vnito/?post_type=speaker&#038;p=533',	8,	'speaker',	'',	0),
