(559,	1,	'2015-01-09 08:52:07',	'2015-01-09 08:52:07',	'Mr. Long Vuong has been working for LogiGear for 6 years as Head of HR. While helping the Company acquiring and growing a quality and scalable workforce, now at 800 headcounts, he has been actively participating in IT/software community when representing LogiGear to HCA, QTSC, VINASA, AMCHAM, and SE/CS schools in HCMC and Danang, Vietnam. He was a member of the Organizing Board for VISTACON (Vietnam International Software Testing &amp; Automation Conference) for 2010, 2011, 2013, hosted by LogiGear &amp; HCA (2013).\r\n\r\nInterestingly, although Mr. Vuong is serving in human resources, his solid background is Finance &amp; Accounting with more than 20 years experience. Aside from that, he makes his hobby as a free-lance translator/editor with a proud “fortune” of more than 30 books published in Vietnamese, such as The Snowball, Classic Drucker, Differentiate or Die, The 7 Habits of Highly Effective People, The 8th Habit, The Speed of Trust, The Principle-Centered Leadership, Break-through Thinking, Think &amp; Grow Rich, Nudge, The 24-Carrot Manager, etc.',	'Long Vuong-Bao',	'',	'publish',	'open',	'open',	'',	'long-vuong-bao',	'',	'',	'2015-01-21 17:12:34',	'2015-01-21 17:12:34',	'',	0,	'https://nhunguyen-nhunguyen1980.c9.io/Vnito/?post_type=speaker&#038;p=559',	12,	'speaker',	'',	0),
