(568,	1,	'2015-01-09 08:56:42',	'2015-01-09 08:56:42',	'<strong>Biography:</strong>\r\nIn Febrary, 2013 to present: Vu Anh Tuan has become General Secretary of HCMC Computer Association (HCA)\r\nFrom March, 2012 to present: Mr. Tuan is Director of HCA – ITP company.\r\nFrom March, 2012 to Febrary, 2013: Mr. Tuan was Deputy General Secretary  of HCA\r\nFrom 2006 to present: Be the Chairman of Cuu Long Computer company.\r\nFrom 2011 to 2012: Mr. Tuan was Business Development Director, IDC Trading company in HCMC (IDC Group – Hanoi)\r\nFrom 2007 to 2008: Mr. Tuan was Deputy Director of  CMS2 Company\r\nFrom 2000 to 2004: Mr. Tuan was Managing director of  MEKONG GREEN CORP.\r\n<strong>Tuan has built  and developed succesfully on First computer brand MEKONGGREEN in Vietnam with over 300 dealers spreading from North / Central / West Central / South</strong>\r\nFrom 1995 to 2000: Be Director, VT&amp;T Company.\r\nFrom 1992  to  1995: Be Director, EIE company in HCM city branch.',	'Tuan Vu-Anh',	'',	'inherit',	'open',	'open',	'',	'540-revision-v1',	'',	'',	'2015-01-09 08:56:42',	'2015-01-09 08:56:42',	'',	540,	'https://nhunguyen-nhunguyen1980.c9.io/Vnito/2015/01/540-revision-v1/',	0,	'revision',	'',	0),
(569,	1,	'2015-01-09 08:58:24',	'2015-01-09 08:58:24',	'Biography (short brief in 200 words): Mr. An Mai has been working in ICT industry for more than 18 years. He has extensive experience in setting up and operating Offshore Development Centers for enterprises from early-stage to Fortune 500. An also has international working experience in USA, Canada and APAC countries. He is a serial entrepreneur and involved in several startups in mobile application and IT service fields. In 2008, An co-founded IMT Solutions, a technology service firm focusing on providing software offshore services for Independent Software Vendors (ISV) and small and medium enterprises globally. An obtained his master degrees in both engineering and business administration. An is one of the early adopters of Agile Scrum in Vietnam.',	'An Mai-Hoai',	'',	'inherit',	'open',	'open',	'',	'513-revision-v1',	'',	'',	'2015-01-09 08:58:24',	'2015-01-09 08:58:24',	'',	513,	'https://nhunguyen-nhunguyen1980.c9.io/Vnito/2015/01/513-revision-v1/',	0,	'revision',	'',	0),
(570,	1,	'2015-01-09 08:58:39',	'2015-01-09 08:58:39',	'Nhuan had been in software industry since the last 15 years, serving NIIT, a leading Global Talent development Corporation as faculty member, and as a Head of Software Development for Arrive Technologies Vietnam, a US high-tech telecommunications start up.\r\nHe also ran the Software Department for Next Level Communications Vietnam, which has been acquired by Motorola.\r\nNhuan holds the Master Degree in IT Engineering from HCMC University of Technology, Vietnam. He is also a PMP certified by PMI since 2010. Nhuan holds an extensive experience of successfully managing the development of state-of-the-art applications on various domains for the past 15 years in all phases of software development with different roles.\r\nNhuan has brought valuable expertise including telecommunications embedded / real-time software applications development related to PDH, SONET, SDH and Ethernet Inter-networking; applications to trade automatically using successful equity arbitrage strategies on stock exchanges all over the world; applications for content services, requisition and procurement, further business intelligence solutions in the health-care sector to LARION. His multiple expertise and vast experience in the industry is leading the organization at peak.\r\nNhuan is an active executive board member of several associations, including HCA [Ho Chi Minh City Computer Association] and YBAHCM [Ho Chi Minh City Young Businesspeople\'s Association].',	'Lai Duc Nhuan',	'',	'inherit',	'open',	'open',	'',	'24-revision-v1',	'',	'',	'2015-01-09 08:58:39',	'2015-01-09 08:58:39',	'',	24,	'https://nhunguyen-nhunguyen1980.c9.io/Vnito/2015/01/24-revision-v1/',	0,	'revision',	'',	0),
(571,	1,	'2015-01-09 09:01:11',	'2015-01-09 09:01:11',	'Kazuhiro Iwai has been within the IT industry for more than 20 years. A strong emphasis in the area of marketing and business development, sales, corporate and product strategy. Participating in the establishment of ISB Vietnam December 2003, he has been an instrumental figure ever since, mostly involved in the R&D programs where one of his most important contributions is linking ISB Vietnam and Japanese clients, representative and marketing for the Open Embedded System Foundation in Vietnam since 2009. Beside extensive management experience in enterprise, wireless and mobile, security and managed services software, he concurrently became the coordinator with ODM/SoC Taiwanese companies for hardware services.\r\n\r\nParticipating in Vietnam IT Outsourcing conference, Iwai aims to help attending companies maximize their opportunity and potential of this business segment in Japan market, continue promoting offshore development in Vietnam to Japan and expending to ASEAN markets with new technology solutions.\r\n',	'Kazuhiro Iwai',	'',	'publish',	'open',	'open',	'',	'kazuhiro-iwai',	'',	'',	'2015-01-21 17:05:30',	'2015-01-21 17:05:30',	'',	0,	'https://nhunguyen-nhunguyen1980.c9.io/Vnito/?post_type=speaker&#038;p=571',	9,	'speaker',	'',	0),
