(576,	1,	'2015-01-09 09:03:47',	'2015-01-09 09:03:47',	'Quyen Nguyen has more than 10 years of marketing &amp; business development, international sales, management experience in IT and Advertising industry. During those years, she has successfully led start-ups, managed Business Development ’s team &amp; projects, co-developed solutions, brought new solutions to market, created &amp; directed highly successful marketing strategies/campaigns.\r\nFor most of her career has been spent in technical, Quyen joined the Vietnam Outsourcing Club since early 2014, she is now one of the BOM of this organization. ISB Vietnam, a subordinate company of ISB Corporation in Japan, is where she chose to work for. This enables Quyen to utilize her highly developed level of cross-cultural experience and awareness.\r\n\r\nBeing truly international within her areas of expertise, she tends to thrive within new challenges, looking to expanding into new markets either geographically or through expansion of ISB Vietnam’s product ranges.',	'Quyen Nguyen-Thi-Kieu',	'',	'publish',	'open',	'open',	'',	'quyen-nguyen-thi-kieu',	'',	'',	'2015-01-26 12:09:07',	'2015-01-26 12:09:07',	'',	0,	'https://nhunguyen-nhunguyen1980.c9.io/Vnito/?post_type=speaker&#038;p=576',	17,	'speaker',	'',	0),
