(656,	1,	'2015-01-10 16:53:30',	'2015-01-10 16:53:30',	'Nhuan had been in software industry since the last 15 years, serving NIIT, a leading Global Talent development Corporation as faculty member, and as a Head of Software Development for Arrive Technologies Vietnam, a US high-tech telecommunications start up.\r\nHe also ran the Software Department for Next Level Communications Vietnam, which has been acquired by Motorola.\r\nNhuan holds the Master Degree in IT Engineering from HCMC University of Technology, Vietnam. He is also a PMP certified by PMI since 2010. Nhuan holds an extensive experience of successfully managing the development of state-of-the-art applications on various domains for the past 15 years in all phases of software development with different roles.\r\nNhuan has brought valuable expertise including telecommunications embedded / real-time software applications development related to PDH, SONET, SDH and Ethernet Inter-networking; applications to trade automatically using successful equity arbitrage strategies on stock exchanges all over the world; applications for content services, requisition and procurement, further business intelligence solutions in the health-care sector to LARION. His multiple expertise and vast experience in the industry is leading the organization at peak.\r\nNhuan is an active executive board member of several associations, including HCA [Ho Chi Minh City Computer Association] and YBAHCM [Ho Chi Minh City Young Businesspeople\'s Association].',	'Nhuan Lai-Duc',	'',	'inherit',	'open',	'open',	'',	'24-revision-v1',	'',	'',	'2015-01-10 16:53:30',	'2015-01-10 16:53:30',	'',	24,	'https://nhunguyen-nhunguyen1980.c9.io/Vnito/2015/01/24-revision-v1/',	0,	'revision',	'',	0),
