(864,	1,	'2015-01-14 14:20:54',	'2015-01-14 14:20:54',	'PhD Nguyen Cong Ai has been working for KPMG since 1998, in Slovakia and Vietnam. He has been involved in providing Market Entry advisory services to many international companies entering Vietnam.. He is serving as Head of Market Entry Group and  Partner – Ho Chi Minh Office, Tax & Corporate Services. PhD Nguyen Cong Ai has extensive experience in conducting market entry studies, location analysis, commercial due diligence and assistance with Investment licensing and post-license compliance. \r\n\r\nBeing in contact with Government Agencies and Business Communities throughout Vietnam for years, Ai has extensive business and government network.\r\n\r\nDr Ai’s clients include many of leading companies in Vietnam and overseas: Petro Vietnam Fertilizer and Chemicals Company, Kookmin Bank, Lotte Mart, Masan Group Corporation, Vietnam Southern Food General Corporation, Mitsubishi Corporation, Deutsche Bank AG, Sharp Corporation.\r\n',	'Ai Nguyen-Cong',	'',	'inherit',	'open',	'open',	'',	'415-revision-v1',	'',	'',	'2015-01-14 14:20:54',	'2015-01-14 14:20:54',	'',	415,	'https://nhunguyen-nhunguyen1980.c9.io/Vnito/415-revision-v1/',	0,	'revision',	'',	0),
