(893,	5,	'2015-01-15 10:30:53',	'2015-01-15 10:30:53',	'<p>Viet Hung is the Managing Director of KMS Technology Vietnam where he is responsible for the overall operations and growth of the organization. He was one of the co-founders of KMS Technology with the urge to build a workplace where people can grow and become successful. During his journey with KMS, Hung finds that his work is much easier due to the fact that his partners and co-workers at KMS are highly talented individuals, who share with him many values and most importantly the dream to build a great company.</p>\n<p>Viet Hung began his career as a software developer. Then, grew through variety of positions including business analyst, project manager, and engineering manager in the top outsourcing firms in HCMC, Vietnam.</p>\n<p>Viet Hung received a BS degree from Ho Chi Minh University of Technology, majored in Information Technology. He completed his Executive MBA Program at Shidler School of Business (University of Hawaii at Manoa) in 2009.</p>\n',	'Hung Nguyen-Viet',	'',	'inherit',	'open',	'open',	'',	'533-autosave-v1',	'',	'',	'2015-01-15 10:30:53',	'2015-01-15 10:30:53',	'',	533,	'https://nhunguyen-nhunguyen1980.c9.io/Vnito/533-autosave-v1/',	0,	'revision',	'',	0),
