(963,	5,	'2015-01-20 15:58:33',	'2015-01-20 15:58:33',	'General Secretary of HCMC Computer Association (HCA)\n\nMr. Vu Anh Tuan is currently General Secretary of  HCA, where he had been Deputy General Secretary since March 2012.  In addition to the role in HCA, Mr. Tuan is the Director of ITP, a company run by HCA, and Chairman of Cuu Long Computer Company.\n<em><span style=\"text-decoration: underline\">Other milestones</span></em>:\n\n<em>2011 to 2012: Business Development Director, IDC Trading Company in HCMC (IDC Group – Hanoi)\n2007 to 2008: Deputy Director of  CMS2 Company\n2000 to 2004: Managing Director of  MEKONG GREEN CORP. Mr. Tuan has built and successfully developed the first computer brand in Vietnam, MEKONGGREEN, with more than 300 dealers across the country\n1995 to 2000: Director of VT&amp;T Company\n1992  to  1995: Director of EIE Company, HCM City branch.</em>',	'Tuan Vu-Anh',	'',	'inherit',	'open',	'open',	'',	'540-autosave-v1',	'',	'',	'2015-01-20 15:58:33',	'2015-01-20 15:58:33',	'',	540,	'https://nhunguyen-nhunguyen1980.c9.io/Vnito/540-autosave-v1/',	0,	'revision',	'',	0),
