(1001,	5,	'2015-01-27 09:28:48',	'2015-01-27 09:28:48',	'<strong>Frank Schellenberg</strong> is the founder and shareholder of DIGI-TEXX – a successful Business Process Outsourcing Company that has been operating in Vietnam since 2003.\r\n\r\nIn 2004, Mr. Schellenberg founded GHP Far East (now known as Swiss Post Solutions) as a spin-off of DIGI-TEXX for the GHP Group from Germany and led the company as CEO until 2014. He made GHP Far East a leading BPO and Software Development provider in Vietnam.\r\n\r\nHe supports foreign investors to invest in Vietnam and has also invested in other IT related companies including DSG Vietnam, Travel2Pay, RASIA, Saigon IT Partner and BIPS<strong><em>.</em></strong>\r\n\r\nSchellenberg now owns a consulting company, Schellenberg Consulting Ltd<em>. </em>which provides professional technical, finance and legal support for investors in the IT industry. Additionally, he works actively in advisory committees for universities and international schools.\r\n\r\nMr. Schellenberg earned a Master’s degree of Engineering from Friedrich Schiller University Jena in Germany in 1985 and gained his international leadership skills as an IT manager in the publishing and communication industry before he relocated to Vietnam in 2000. He is highly committed to technology and perpetual entrepreneurship.',	'Frank Schellenberg',	'',	'inherit',	'open',	'open',	'',	'431-revision-v1',	'',	'',	'2015-01-27 09:28:48',	'2015-01-27 09:28:48',	'',	431,	'https://nhunguyen-nhunguyen1980.c9.io/Vnito/431-revision-v1/',	0,	'revision',	'',	0),
